title 0.6 - New note (spa)

note over Browser
The event handler "window.onload" 
executes the "form.onsubmit" when
the submit button is clicked 
and follows these steps:

1. Creates a new note.
2. Pushes the note into the notes array.
3. Render all the notes.
4. Sends the new note to the server.
end note

Browser -> Server: HTTP Post https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
